OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy to start, with
OL,6,Fany showers fairly isolated. Some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells developing
OL,8,Fduring the morning, but with a risk of
OL,9,Ffurther isolated showers in the
OL,10,Fafternoon, these dying out later. Warm
OL,11,Fbut breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely dry this evening with
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Remaining dry overnight
OL,15,Fwith clear spells, although cloud
OL,16,Fthickening in northwestern parts
OL,17,Flater. Wind easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
