OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA mostly dry day with sunny
OL,6,Fspells in the south, although thicker
OL,7,Fcloud and patchy rain are likely in
OL,8,Fthe north. Becoming warm, especially
OL,9,Fin the south. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FWarm or
OL,12,Fvery warm during this period, perhaps
OL,13,Fhot on Friday, with sunny spells.
OL,14,FMostly dry, but low risk of heavy
OL,15,Fthundery showers on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
